ed on the wisconsin commissioner of insurances financial advisory council and hmo financial stability task force mr carver received his bachelors of science degree from bradley university and his masters of business administration from the university of wisconsin in addition to mr carver the fortis inc board of directors is composed of the following members anton van rossum chairman mr van rossum is chief executive officer of fortis and chairman of the boards of fortis bank and fortis insurance he is responsible for managing fortis extensive global insurance investment and banking operations prior to joining fortis mr van rossum was a senior partner at mckinsey and company with management responsibility for its brussels office mr van rossum holds a masters degree in economics and business administration from the rotterdam erasmus university hendrik jochem hielkema vicechairman mr hielkema is a member of the board of directors of fortis prior to his current position mr hielkema was vice chairman of the fortis executive committee and chairman of the management committee of fortis insurance nv mr hielkema started his career with fortis in  when he joined the executive board of fortis amev nv formerly nv amev now fortis nv before joining fortis mr hielkema was a senior vice president at chase manhattan bank and chairman of the executive board of nederlandse crediet bank he earned a bachelors degree in business administration from university of oregon and a masters degree of business administration from texas tech robert j blendon dr blendon has been a professor at the harvard school of public health and the kennedy school of government since  previously he served as vice president of the robert wood johnson foundation mr blendon earned his bachelors degree at marietta college in marietta oh he has a masters degree of business administration and an scd from johns hopkins university beth bronner ms bronner is the former president and coo of advo inc the nations largest fullservice targeted direct mail marketing company before her position at advo inc ms bronner was president of the health division at sunbeam corporation she has also held senior management positions at citibank and att ms bronner received a bachelors degree from vassar college and has a masters degree of business administration from the university of chicago she is currently a member of the board of directors of the haincelestial group j kerry clayton mr clayton is the president and chief executive officer of fortis inc previously mr clayton held a variety of management positions at fortis inc including chief financial officer and executive vice president of fortis inc and president of fortis benefits insurance company mr clayton earned an engineering degree from georgia tech and a masters degree of business administration from harvard business school arie aristide fakkert mr fakkert is general manager fortis international nv prior to assuming his current position mr fakkert served as the general manager amev praktijkvoorziening nv mr fakkert began his career at royal dutch shell group serving in the us and the uk he has a masters degree in business from rotterdam erasmus university allen r freedman mr freedman joined fortis inc as its first president in  and retired from his position as chairman and ceo in  with over three decades in the financial services industry mr freedmans experience includes banking venture investing and tax law mr freedman has an undergraduate degree from tufts university and a law degree from the university of virginia he has been chairman of systems  computer technology corp the leading provider of infrastructure software to the higher education marketplace since january  h carroll mackin mr mackin was an executive vice president at fortis inc from  to  before joining the company he was director for investments at forstmann leff mr mackin has a bachelors degree from georgia institute of technology and a masters degree of business administration from the university of pennsylvanias wharton school john michael palms dr palms has been president of the university of south carolina since  earlier in his career dr palms served as president of georgia state university and was a professor and administrator at emory university dr palms received a bachelors degree in physics from the citadel he received his masters degree in physics from emory university and his phd from the university of new mexico dr palms also serves on the boards of exelon corporation computer tasks group simcom corporation and is chairman of the board of the institute for defense analysis georges valckenaere before retiring from fortis as advisor to the chief executive officer in january  mr georges valckenaere was chief excutive officer of fortis international before joining fortis international mr valckenaere was director  general manager of fortis ag in addition to serving on the fortis inc and fortis international boards of directors mr valckenaere also served on the boards of fortis bank amevvsb aslkcger bank and caifor georges valckenaere holds a masters degree in mathematics and a masters degree in actuarial science from katholieke universiteit leuven kul about fortis inc fortis inc is a financial services company that through its operating companies and affiliates has built leadership positions in a number of specialty insurance market segments in the us the companies of fortis inc are leading providers of individual temporary and small group health insurance group disability life and dental insurance preneed funeral insurance credit related insurance products and services and membership and extended service programs for more information visit the companys website at httpwwwusfortiscom fortis inc is part of fortis an international financial services provider active in the fields of insurance banking and investment fortis employs approximately  people worldwide and offers a broad range of financial services in its home market the benelux countries fortis occupies a leading position and offers a broad range of financial services to individuals companies and the public sector outside its home market fortis concentrates on selected market segments fortis had total assets in excess of  billion as one of the worlds largest financial services companies fortis ranks st based on assets and rd based on revenues on the fortune global  and nd based on revenues on the forbes international  list july   media contact melissa kivett fortis inc  melissakivettusfortiscom next razorfish and fortis inc launch redesigned financial services web site howard l carver  gastonia nc  intelius sign in we found howard l carver in gastonia nc howard l carver intelius found that howard l carver is a male between  and  years old from gastonia nc we have connected them to  address  phone and  relatives or associates get report now age howard l carver is in his s howard has lived in gastonia nc howards relatives margaret carver thelma carver lonnie carver howard l carver zodiac signvirgo gendermale get report now want to know more about howard get a comprehensive background report find full phone numbers and other contact information when available all from billions of available public records continue below for more details about howard or use our people search engine to find others get background check on howard l carver get a criminal check on howard l carver get a public record report on howard l carver get a people search report on howard l carver howard l carvers contact information known cities lived in find out where howard l carver has lived as well as howard l carvers phone numbers and email addresses howard l carver has lived in  states north carolina address for howard l carver  c s gastonia nc has lived in gastonia nc get full address report phone numbers associated with howard l carver    gastonia nc get full phone report email addresses associated with howard l carver get email report howard l carvers social ne